{"tid":1766313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警世：香港人既善良唔可以比人利用","createTime":"2019-12-02T13:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T02:54:36.000Z","uid":118431,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2efc299ef98c5c68f0ae01fb2c204200e40db725","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"（代朋友Post, 以下為朋友親身經歷)<br />\n<br />\n剛才係屯門市中心比個普通話人截停，對方係男人，身高目測175cm，大概35-40歲，衣著斯斯文文，以下係我地對話：<br />\n<br />\n男人：美女，不好意思，我現在想去尖沙嘴......<br />\n<br />\n我（以為佢要問路）：你要坐巴士還是地鐵？<br />\n<br />\n男人：你先聽我說完。我家人他們都在尖沙嘴那邊，他們去了澳門那邊玩，在那邊賭場玩百家樂什麼的，現在在港澳碼頭那邊......（下刪一萬字）我坐地鐵、巴士，還是taxi都行，問題是我現在身上沒有money了，就是錢......<br />\n<br />\n我（未等佢講完）：哦！ 你可以去地鐵那邊，只要你拿證件登記，就可以讓你免費搭乘一次。<br />\n<br />\n男人：世界是會有這樣免費的事嗎！<br />\n<br />\n我：真的！<br />\n<br />\n男人：nonono! 你看能幫就幫，不能幫就走吧！<br />\n<br />\n跟住就即刻走左。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下係朋友的見解：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n首先，我有一年去上海旅行，係浦東機場親身經歷過幾乎一模一樣的騙案。類似都係話身上無錢，要借錢搭車，不過我果次仲借左高鐵車票錢比佢，但我覺得我去人地地頭被騙，咁算，我自己攞來衰！但<strong>而家佢地行入香港呃香港人，就一定唔得！</strong><br />\n強烈建議大家千萬不要因為一時善心二而亂幫人，你的善心只會助長騙案繼續增加，到時真正需要的人就無人幫！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所以，你的善良必須要聰明！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議可以用以下方式：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 帶佢到地鐵站，幫佢買飛，送埋佢入閘，唔好比張飛佢，有機會拎去退錢。<br />\n2. 帶佢到巴士站，巴士來到幫佢嘟八達通/入錢。<br />\n3. 好似我咁，同佢講地鐵可以用證件登記借票搭一次。（港鐵真係有賒票制度，可以參考返呢則新聞報導：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160526/bkn-20160526070043058-0526_00822_001.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160526%2Fbkn-20160526070043058-0526_00822_001.html%EF%BC%89&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=06c00f88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160526/bkn-20160526070043058-0526_00822_001.html）</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>通常你提出以上方案，如果係騙徒，就會即刻離開，唔再纏住你；如果係真係需要幫忙，一定唔會拒絕。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請求各位大大幫推，提醒更多善良既香港人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42a3cce36d6daa86b70e4659c32d07630441aef","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:09:09.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"0b557e9c9bf472f75cce93de7fb69f472b68affe","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:09:21.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"46dc039bac53cd157ba883449f06d7eaad3044a5","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"aa084bb51d925c148d64ab3d781816ae468d30e4","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"31760e46c12deafdccc27f5ca263742c1ce187bd","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"cbea2feb47567123c99b871948b3742893aff91a","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"d9f1075a4499bf009adb01994135bc333ad6b3a8","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"69e09d9e38fe241d47696f36d9bfb1f416adc06c","tid":1766313,"uid":118431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12